channel.title: Solar Sailor - Tropical Remix
channel.description:
Hello everyone. If you’ve seen Tron Legacy, then you probably know this song. Remade all on Auxy with some added touches.
This song has a nice wavy tone with nice drum patterns and some good bass.
Soundcloud: [Solar Sailor](https://soundcloud.com/tropical_madman/solar-sailor-tropical-remix)
